headline: UBS sees agricultural cycle near bottom as it upgrades Deere
summary: Investing.com -- UBS raised its rating on Deere & Co to Buy from Neutral on expectations that the agricultural machinery downcycle is approaching its end and that earnings are set to recover in 2027. The firm lowered its price target to $535 from $545.
